title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ and RP on Higgins Helitours Money Laundering
content:
Utilize your fleet of sightseeing helicopters to recover and reclaim lost cargo in Higgins Helitours Money Laundering Missions, paying out Double Rewards to daring pilots through July 2.

Players looking to get into the aviation tourism business can do so after purchasing the Hands On Car Wash from Maze Bank Foreclosures.
